thread.title: Augusta National Still Has Bite

author: Brian Costa
title: Augusta National Still Has Bite

organizations.name: augusta national still has bite augusta

text:
Augusta, Ga
Rory McIlroy arrived at Augusta National more than a week before the start of the Masters. By the time the tournament began Thursday, he had played 90 practice holes, the equivalent of five full rounds. In pursuit of the only major he has never won, McIlroy studied the course more extensively than ever.
Then he teed off, and...
